task.persona: An art historian studying the depictions of weapons in medieval artwork

instruction.level1: Schedule a research meeting on May 18th to discuss the depiction of crossbows in 14th-century Persian manuscripts
instruction.level2: Schedule a meeting on May 18th titled "Depiction of Crossbows in 14th-Century Persian Manuscripts."
instruction.level3: Schedule a meeting titled 'Depiction of Crossbows in 14th-Century Persian Manuscripts' on May 18th from 10:00 AM to 11:00 AM.

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new event
Select 'Event' from the menu to initiate creating a new event.
Fill in the event title with 'Depiction of Crossbows in 14th-Century Persian Manuscripts'.
Click the date field to change the event date to May 18th.
Fill in the start date with 'Sunday, May 18'
Fill in the start time with '10:00 AM'.
Fill in the end time with '11:00 AM'.
Click the 'Save' button to finalize the creation of the event.
